{"tid":475254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣臭豆腐登紐時 中國網友怒：臭豆腐是中國的","createTime":"2017-11-21T03:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T07:09:39.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"02d22efccb4b50f8bd55667ae82c10967d6caeb6","tid":475254,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:14:30.000Z","msg":"台灣臭豆腐登紐時 陸網友怒：臭豆腐是中國的<br />\n<br />\n2017-11-21 07:10聯合報 記者楊德宜╱即時報導<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/11/21/1/4265011.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F1%2F4265011.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=aa086b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王丹在臉書分享紐約時報報導戴記獨臭之家的報導，並稱讚「台灣美食，走上國際」，鼓勵用「軟實力」讓國際社會看到台灣是可行的路。圖擷自「王丹网站 Wang Dans Page」臉書 facebook<br />\n<br />\n台灣的臭豆腐國際有名！六四學運領袖王丹昨晚在臉書表示，紐約時報用半版篇幅介紹台灣美食「戴記臭豆腐」。台灣美食，走上國際。「其實，用軟實力讓國際社會看到台灣，是完全可以走得通的大路」。但有大陸網友不滿他的「台灣美食」發言 ，留言批可笑，指臭豆腐「是中國美食，不是台灣美食，别亂吃豆腐」。<br />\n<br />\n王丹在臉書分享紐約時報報導戴記獨臭之家的報導，並稱讚「台灣美食，走上國際」，鼓勵用「軟實力」讓國際社會看到台灣是可行的路。一席話讓大陸網友「森七七」了，留言嗆聲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/2830506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F2830506&d=YHB6s8ga2I4eb32L6MIQwP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=196a184d\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/2830506</a>"},{"pid":"04f5208940b8210fd8fa15b9e2190e5aedbf1501","tid":475254,"uid":35790,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"即係話台灣唔係中國一部份"},{"pid":"4b42026e122293599c72c117ff8c0e66c4d61ce0","tid":475254,"uid":55391,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:15:54.000Z","msg":"既然台灣係中國一部分<br />\n咁登報咪又係即係中國嘅<br />\n有咩好玻璃心？！"},{"pid":"0eb4aa276f96164f3302b3f556eb595a3eafc505","tid":475254,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"呢班支那畜又分裂中国了。<br />\n<br />\n點解變咗臺灣唔係中国了？"},{"pid":"364e59ac92099a096bd9b14241a3e420de968063","tid":475254,"uid":119778,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:17:27.000Z","msg":"雞蛋仔都變左台灣<br />\nn年前都會加港式兩隻字，而家索性叫雞蛋糕算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4560579767a0c5d2042a3c5a26d104785c94b1b5","tid":475254,"uid":10079,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:18:01.000Z","msg":"又話台灣係中國一部分，又要係到吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdb8f18ad0dc8789ef67a1aa663866ca5f9add2","tid":475254,"uid":36152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"全宇宙都係支那，連外星人都要學支那話"},{"pid":"b662e7118896c3d62e0d4782a034a9fe182622d8","tid":475254,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"好亂呀。<br />\n<br />\n又話臺灣係中国，點解臭豆腐係臺灣，又變咗唔係中国？<br />\n<br />\n外國人睇到一頭霧水。"},{"pid":"d3d054495ca21481bc9b3fe7525e7891d2762ade","tid":475254,"uid":42509,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"我一直以為臭豆腐係香港"},{"pid":"b3fa64950147ffb8a006422fa59150c6df9e1fec","tid":475254,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"超市常見中國生產食品<br />\n寫住&quot;韓式xxx  日式xxxx&quot;"},{"pid":"113fa67c2badb15c5bbd6d723bb61da2e2748a66","tid":475254,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:21:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一直以為臭豆腐係香港</blockquote><br />\n台灣同港式臭豆腐唔同架"},{"pid":"5499dcbab4be64f2d3b787b94b645f52044945e1","tid":475254,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超市常見中國生產食品<br />\n寫住&quot;韓式xxx  日式xxxx&quot;</blockquote><br />\n建議台灣寫&quot;中國式臭豆腐&quot;"},{"pid":"ed657366a99adffd61c3c57dc297637b724b